ground-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Bootstrap 使用了一些 HTML5 元素和 CSS 属性。为了让这些正常工作，您需要使用 HTML5 文档类型（Doctype）。 因此，请在使用 Bootstrap 项目的开头包含下面的代码段。</p><pre class=\"prettyprint\" style=\"border-width: 1px 1px 1px 4px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(221, 221, 221); margin: 15px auto; padding: 10px 15px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: 20px; font-family: &#39;courier new&#39;; word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background: url(http://www.runoob.com/images/codecolorer_bg.gif) 50% 0% rgb(251, 251, 251);\">&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;\r\n&lt;html&gt;\r\n....\r\n&lt;/html&gt;</pre><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-size: 12px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">如果在 Bootstrap 创建的网页开头不使用 HTML5 的文档类型（Doctype），您可能会面临一些浏览器显示不一致的问题，甚至可能面临一些特定情境下的不一致，以致于您的代码不能通过 W3C 标准的验证。</p><h2 class=\"tutheader\" style=\"border-width: 1px 0px 0px; border-top-style: solid; border-top-color: rgb(212, 212, 212); margin: 0px; padding: 5px 0px 0px; font-size: 1.8em; line-height: 1.8em; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">移动设备优先</h2><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-size: 12px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">移动设备优先是 Bootstrap 3 的最显著的变化。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-size: 12px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">在之前的 Bootstrap 版本中（直到 2.x），您需要手动引用另一个 CSS，才能让整个项目友好的支持移动设备。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-size: 12px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">现在不一样了，Bootstrap 3 默认的 CSS 本身就对移动设备友好支持。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-size: 12px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Bootstrap 3 的设计目标是移动设备优先，然后才是桌面设备。这实际上是一个非常及时的转变，因为现在越来越多的用户使用移动设备。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-size: 12px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">为了让 Bootstrap 开发的网站对移动设备友好，确保适当的绘制和触屏缩放，需要在网页的 head 之中添加<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">viewport meta</strong><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>标签，如下所示：</p><pre class=\"prettyprint\" style=\"border-width: 1px 1px 1px 4px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(221, 221, 221); margin: 15px auto; padding: 10px 15px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: 20px; font-family: &#39;courier new&#39;; word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background: url(http://www.runoob.com/images/codecolorer_bg.gif) 50% 0% rgb(251, 251, 251);\">&lt;meta name=&quot;viewport&quot; content=&quot;width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0&quot;&gt;</pre><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-size: 12px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><em style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">width</em><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>属性控制设备的宽度。假设您的网站将被带有不同屏幕分辨率的设备浏览，那么将它设置为<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><em style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">device-width</em><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>可以确保它能正确呈现在不同设备上。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-size: 12px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><em style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">initial-scale=1.0</em><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>确保网页加载时，以 1:1 的比例呈现，不会有任何的缩放。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-size: 12px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">在移动设备浏览器上，通过为<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">viewport meta</strong><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>标签添加<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><em style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">user-scalable=no</em><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>可以禁用其缩放（zooming）功能。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-size: 12px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">通常情况下，<em style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">maximum-scale=1.0</em><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>与 user-scalable=no 一起使用。这样禁用缩放功能后，用户只能滚动屏幕，就能让您的网站看上去更像原生应用的感觉。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-size: 12px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">注意，这种方式我们并不推荐所有网站使用，还是要看您自己的情况而定！</p><pre class=\"prettyprint\" style=\"border-width: 1px 1px 1px 4px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(221, 221, 221); margin: 15px auto; padding: 10px 15px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: 20px; font-family: &#39;courier new&#39;; word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background: url(http://www.runoob.com/images/codecolorer_bg.gif) 50% 0% rgb(251, 251, 251);\">&lt;meta name=&quot;viewport&quot; content=&quot;width=device-width, \r\n                                     initial-scale=1.0, \r\n                                     maximum-scale=1.0, \r\n                                     user-scalable=no&quot;&gt;</pre><h2 class=\"tutheader\" style=\"border-width: 1px 0px 0px; border-top-style: solid; border-top-color: rgb(212, 212, 212); margin: 0px; padding: 5px 0px 0px; font-size: 1.8em; line-height: 1.8em; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">响应式图像</h2><pre class=\"prettyprint\" style=\"border-width: 1px 1px 1px 4px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(221, 221, 221); margin: 15px auto; padding: 10px 15px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: 20px; font-family: &#39;courier new&#39;; word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background: url(http://www.runoob.com/images/codecolorer_bg.gif) 50% 0% rgb(251, 251, 251);\">&lt;img src=&quot;...&quot; class=&quot;img-responsive&quot; alt=&quot;响应式图像&quot;&gt;</pre><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-size: 12px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">通过添加<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><em style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">img-responsive</em><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>class 可以让 Bootstrap 3 中的图像对响应式布局的支持更友好。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-size: 12px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">接下来让我们看下这个 class 包含了哪些 css 属性。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-size: 12px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">在下面的代码中，可以看到<em style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">img-responsive</em><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>class 为图像赋予了 max-width: 100%; 和 height: auto; 属性，可以让图像按比例缩放，不超过其父元素的尺寸。</p><pre class=\"prettyprint\" style=\"border-width: 1px 1px 1px 4px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(221, 221, 221); margin: 15px auto; padding: 10px 15px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: 20px; font-family: &#39;courier new&#39;; word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background: url(http://www.runoob.com/images/codecolorer_bg.gif) 50% 0% rgb(251, 251, 251);\">.img-responsive {\r\n  display: inline-block;\r\n  height: auto;\r\n  max-width: 100%;\r\n}</pre><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-size: 12px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">这表明相关的图像呈现为<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><em style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">inline-block</em>。当您把元素的 display 属性设置为 inline-block，元素相对于它周围的内容以内联形式呈现，但与内联不同的是，这种情况下我们可以设置宽度和高度。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-size: 12px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">设置<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><em style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">height:auto</em>，相关元素的高度取决于浏览器。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-size: 12px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">设置<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><em style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">max-width</em><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>为 100% 会重写任何通过 width 属性指定的宽度。这让图片对响应式布局的支持更友好。</p><h2 class=\"tutheader\" style=\"border-width: 1px 0px 0px; border-top-style: solid; border-top-color: rgb(212, 212, 212); margin: 0px; padding: 5px 0px 0px; font-size: 1.8em; line-height: 1.8em; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">全局显示、排版和链接</h2><h3 style=\"border: 0px; margin: 8px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 1.4em; font-weight: 700; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">基本的全局显示</h3><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-size: 12px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Bootstrap 3 使用<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><em style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">body {margin: 0;}</em><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>来移除 body 的边距。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-size: 12px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">请看下面有关 body 的设置：</p><pre name=\"code\" class=\"css prettyprint\" style=\"border-width: 1px 1px 1px 4px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(221, 221, 221); margin: 15px auto; padding: 10px 15px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: 20px; font-family: &#39;courier new&#39;; word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background: url(http://www.runoob.com/images/codecolorer_bg.gif) 50% 0% rgb(251, 251, 251);\">body {\r\n  font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\r\n  font-size: 14px;\r\n  line-height: 1.428571429;\r\n  color: #333333;\r\n  background-color: #ffffff;\r\n}</pre><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-size: 12px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">第一条规则设置 body 的默认字体样式为<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><em style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif</em>。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-size: 12px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">第二条规则设置文本的默认字体大小为 14 像素。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-size: 12px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">第三条规则设置默认的行高度为 1.428571429。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-size: 12px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">第四条规则设置默认的文本颜色为 #333333。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-size: 12px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">最后一条规则设置默认的背景颜色为白色。</p><h3 style=\"border: 0px; margin: 8px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 1.4em; font-weight: 700; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">排版</h3><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-size: 12px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">使用 @font-family-base、 @font-size-base 和 @line-height-base 属性作为排版样式。</p><h3 style=\"border: 0px; margin: 8px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 1.4em; font-weight: 700; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">链接样式</h3><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-size: 12px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">通过属性 @link-color 设置全局链接的颜色。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-size: 12px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">对于链接的默认样式，如下设置：</p><pre name=\"code\" class=\"css prettyprint\" style=\"border-width: 1px 1px 1px 4px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(221, 221, 221); margin: 15px auto; padding: 10px 15px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: 20px; font-family: &#39;courier new&#39;; word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background: url(http://www.runoob.com/images/codecolorer_bg.gif) 50% 0% rgb(251, 251, 251);\">a:hover,\r\na:focus {\r\n  color: #2a6496;\r\n  text-decoration: underline;\r\n}\r\n\r\na:focus {\r\n  outline: thin dotted #333;\r\n  outline: 5px auto -webkit-focus-ring-color;\r\n  outline-offset: -2px;\r\n}</pre><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-size: 12px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">所以，当鼠标悬停在链接上，或者点击过的链接，颜色会被设置为 #2a6496。同时，会呈现一条下划线。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-size: 12px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">除此之外，点击过的链接，会呈现一个颜色码为 #333 的细的虚线轮廓。另一条规则是设置轮廓为 5 像素宽，且对于基于 webkit 浏览器有一个<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><em style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">-webkit-focus-ring-color</em><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>的浏览器扩展。轮廓偏移设置为 -2 像素。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-size: 12px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">以上所有这些样式都可以在 scaffolding.less 中找到。</p><h2 class=\"tutheader\" style=\"border-width: 1px 0px 0px; border-top-style: solid; border-top-color: rgb(212, 212, 212); margin: 0px; padding: 5px 0px 0px; font-size: 1.8em; line-height: 1.8em; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">避免跨浏览器的不一致</h2><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-size: 12px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Bootstrap 使用<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://necolas.github.io/normalize.css/\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(100, 133, 76); text-decoration: underline; -webkit-transition: opacity 0.2s; transition: opacity 0.2s;\">Normalize</a><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>来建立跨浏览器的一致性。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-size: 12px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Normalize.css 是一个很小的 CSS 文件，在 HTML 元素的默认样式中提供了更好的跨浏览器一致性。</p><h2 class=\"tutheader\" style=\"border-width: 1px 0px 0px; border-top-style: solid; border-top-color: rgb(212, 212, 212); margin: 0px; padding: 5px 0px 0px; font-size: 1.8em; line-height: 1.8em; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">容器（Container）</h2><pre class=\"prettyprint\" style=\"border-width: 1px 1px 1px 4px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(221, 221, 221); margin: 15px auto; padding: 10px 15px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: 20px; font-family: &#39;courier new&#39;; word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background: url(http://www.runoob.com/images/codecolorer_bg.gif) 50% 0% rgb(251, 251, 251);\">&lt;div class=&quot;container&quot;&gt;\r\n  ...\r\n&lt;/div&gt;</pre><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-size: 12px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Bootstrap 3 的<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><em style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">container</em><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>class 用于包裹页面上的内容。让我们一起来看看 bootstrap.css 文件中的这个<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><em style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">.container</em><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>class。</p><pre name=\"code\" class=\"css prettyprint\" style=\"border-width: 1px 1px 1px 4px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(221, 221, 221); margin: 15px auto; padding: 10px 15px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: 20px; font-family: &#39;courier new&#39;; word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background: url(http://www.runoob.com/images/codecolorer_bg.gif) 50% 0% rgb(251, 251, 251);\">.container {\r\n   padding-right: 15px;\r\n   padding-left: 15px;\r\n   margin-right: auto;\r\n   margin-left: auto;\r\n}</pre><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-size: 12px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">通过上面的代码，把 container 的左右外边距（margin-right、margin-left）交由浏览器决定。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-size: 12px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">请注意，由于内边距（padding）是固定宽度，默认情况下容器是不可嵌套的。</p><pre name=\"code\" class=\"css prettyprint\" style=\"border-width: 1px 1px 1px 4px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(221, 221, 221); margin: 15px auto; padding: 10px 15px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: 20px; font-family: &#39;courier new&#39;; word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background: url(http://www.runoob.com/images/codecolorer_bg.gif) 50% 0% rgb(251, 251, 251);\">.container:before,\r\n.container:after {\r\n  display: table;\r\n  content: &quot; &quot;;\r\n}</pre><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-size: 12px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">这会产生伪元素。设置<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><em style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">display</em><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>为<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><em style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">table</em>，会创建一个匿名的 table-cell 和一个新的块格式化上下文。<em style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">:before</em><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>伪元素防止上边距崩塌，<em style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">:after</em><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>伪元素清除浮动。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-size: 12px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">如果<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><em style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">conteneditable</em><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>属性出现在 HTML 中，由于一些 Opera bug，围绕上述元素创建一个空格。这可以通过使用<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><em style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">content: &quot; &quot;</em><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>来修复。</p><pre name=\"code\" class=\"css prettyprint\" style=\"border-width: 1px 1px 1px 4px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(221, 221, 221); margin: 15px auto; padding: 10px 15px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: 20px; font-family: &#39;courier new&#39;; word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background: url(http://www.runoob.com/images/codecolorer_bg.gif) 50% 0% rgb(251, 251, 251);\">.container:after {\r\n  clear: both;\r\n}</pre><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-size: 12px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">它创建了一个伪元素，并确保了所有的容器包含所有的浮动元素。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-size: 12px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Bootstrap 3 CSS 有一个申请响应的媒体查询，在不同的媒体查询阈值范围内都为 container 设置了max-width，用以匹配网格系统。</p><pre name=\"code\" class=\"css prettyprint\" style=\"border-width: 1px 1px 1px 4px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(221, 221, 221); margin: 15px auto; padding: 10px 15px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: 20px; font-family: &#39;courier new&#39;; word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background: url(http://www.runoob.com/images/codecolorer_bg.gif) 50% 0% rgb(251, 251, 251);\">@media (min-width: 768px) {\r\n   .container {\r\n      width: 750px;\r\n}</pre><hr style=\"color: rgb(212, 212, 212); height: 1px; border: 0px; clear: both; font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(212, 212, 212);\"/><h2 style=\"border: 0px; margin: 2px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 1.8em; line-height: 1.8em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-fam