的 HTML 标签和扩展的类即可创建出不同样式的表单。</p></div><h2 class=\"tutheader\" style=\"border-width: 1px 0px 0px; border-top-style: solid; border-top-color: rgb(212, 212, 212); margin: 0px; padding: 5px 0px 0px; font-size: 1.8em; line-height: 1.8em; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">表单布局</h2><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-size: 12px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Bootstrap 提供了下列类型的表单布局：</p><ul class=\"list\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 1em 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 16.7999992370605px; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><li style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 1em 1em; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.5em; line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 1em; background-image: url(http://www.runoob.com/wp-content/themes/runoob/assets/img/bullet.png); background-position: 0% 0.5em; background-repeat: no-repeat;\">垂直表单（默认）</li><li style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 1em 1em; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.5em; line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 1em; background-image: url(http://www.runoob.com/wp-content/themes/runoob/assets/img/bullet.png); background-position: 0% 0.5em; background-repeat: no-repeat;\">内联表单</li><li style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 1em 1em; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.5em; line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 1em; background-image: url(http://www.runoob.com/wp-content/themes/runoob/assets/img/bullet.png); background-position: 0% 0.5em; background-repeat: no-repeat;\">水平表单</li></ul><h3 style=\"border: 0px; margin: 8px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 1.4em; font-weight: 700; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">垂直或基本表单</h3><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-size: 12px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">基本的表单结构是 Bootstrap 自带的，个别的表单控件自动接收一些全局样式。下面列出了创建基本表单的步骤：</p><ul class=\"list\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 1em 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 16.7999992370605px; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><li style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 1em 1em; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.5em; line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 1em; background-image: url(http://www.runoob.com/wp-content/themes/runoob/assets/img/bullet.png); background-position: 0% 0.5em; background-repeat: no-repeat;\">向父 &lt;form&gt; 元素添加<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><em>role=&quot;form&quot;</em>。</li><li style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 1em 1em; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.5em; line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 1em; background-image: url(http://www.runoob.com/wp-content/themes/runoob/assets/img/bullet.png); background-position: 0% 0.5em; background-repeat: no-repeat;\">把标签和控件放在一个带有 class<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><em>.form-group</em><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>的 &lt;div&gt; 中。这是获取最佳间距所必需的。</li><li style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 1em 1em; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.5em; line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 1em; background-image: url(http://www.runoob.com/wp-content/themes/runoob/assets/img/bullet.png); background-position: 0% 0.5em; background-repeat: no-repeat;\">向所有的文本元素 &lt;input&gt;、&lt;textarea&gt; 和 &lt;select&gt; 添加 class<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><em>.form-control</em>。</li></ul><pre class=\"prettyprint tryit\" style=\"border-width: 1px 1px 1px 4px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(221, 221, 221); margin: 15px auto; padding: 10px 15px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: 20px; font-family: &#39;courier new&#39;; word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background: url(http://www.runoob.com/images/codecolorer_bg.gif) 50% 0% rgb(251, 251, 251);\">&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;\r\n&lt;html&gt;\r\n&lt;head&gt;\r\n   &lt;title&gt;Bootstrap 实例 - 基本表单&lt;/title&gt;\r\n   &lt;link rel=&quot;stylesheet&quot; href=&quot;http://apps.bdimg.com/libs/bootstrap/3.3.0/css/bootstrap.min.css&quot;&gt;\r\n   &lt;script src=&quot;http://apps.bdimg.com/libs/jquery/2.1.1/jquery.min.js&quot;&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n   &lt;script src=&quot;http://apps.bdimg.com/libs/bootstrap/3.3.0/js/bootstrap.min.js&quot;&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n&lt;/head&gt;\r\n&lt;body&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;form role=&quot;form&quot;&gt;\r\n   &lt;div class=&quot;form-group&quot;&gt;\r\n      &lt;label for=&quot;name&quot;&gt;名称&lt;/label&gt;\r\n      &lt;input type=&quot;text&quot; class=&quot;form-control&quot; id=&quot;name&quot; \r\n         placeholder=&quot;请输入名称&quot;&gt;\r\n   &lt;/div&gt;\r\n   &lt;div class=&quot;form-group&quot;&gt;\r\n      &lt;label for=&quot;inputfile&quot;&gt;文件输入&lt;/label&gt;\r\n      &lt;input type=&quot;file&quot; id=&quot;inputfile&quot;&gt;\r\n      &lt;p class=&quot;help-block&quot;&gt;这里是块级帮助文本的实例。&lt;/p&gt;\r\n   &lt;/div&gt;\r\n   &lt;div class=&quot;checkbox&quot;&gt;\r\n      &lt;label&gt;\r\n      &lt;input type=&quot;checkbox&quot;&gt; 请打勾\r\n      &lt;/label&gt;\r\n   &lt;/div&gt;\r\n   &lt;button type=&quot;submit&quot; class=&quot;btn btn-default&quot;&gt;提交&lt;/button&gt;\r\n&lt;/form&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;/body&gt;\r\n&lt;/html&gt;</pre><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-size: 12px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">结果如下所示：</p><div class=\"cover\" style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(214, 214, 214); margin: 0px; padding: 5px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"http://www.runoob.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/basicform_demo.jpg\" alt=\"基本表单\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto;\"/></div><h3 style=\"border: 0px; margin: 8px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 1.4em; font-weight: 700; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">内联表单</h3><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-size: 12px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">如果需要创建一个表单，它的所有元素是内联的，向左对齐的，标签是并排的，请向 &lt;form&gt; 标签添加 class<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><em>.form-inline</em>。</p><pre class=\"prettyprint tryit\" style=\"border-width: 1px 1px 1px 4px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(221, 221, 221); margin: 15px auto; padding: 10px 15px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: 20px; font-family: &#39;courier new&#39;; word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background: url(http://www.runoob.com/images/codecolorer_bg.gif) 50% 0% rgb(251, 251, 251);\">&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;\r\n&lt;html&gt;\r\n&lt;head&gt;\r\n   &lt;title&gt;Bootstrap 实例 - 内联表单&lt;/title&gt;\r\n   &lt;link rel=&quot;stylesheet&quot; href=&quot;http://apps.bdimg.com/libs/bootstrap/3.3.0/css/bootstrap.min.css&quot;&gt;\r\n   &lt;script src=&quot;http://apps.bdimg.com/libs/jquery/2.1.1/jquery.min.js&quot;&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n   &lt;script src=&quot;http://apps.bdimg.com/libs/bootstrap/3.3.0/js/bootstrap.min.js&quot;&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n&lt;/head&gt;\r\n&lt;body&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;form class=&quot;form-inline&quot; role=&quot;form&quot;&gt;\r\n   &lt;div class=&quot;form-group&quot;&gt;\r\n      &lt;label class=&quot;sr-only&quot; for=&quot;name&quot;&gt;名称&lt;/label&gt;\r\n      &lt;input type=&quot;text&quot; class=&quot;form-control&quot; id=&quot;name&quot; \r\n         placeholder=&quot;请输入名称&quot;&gt;\r\n   &lt;/div&gt;\r\n   &lt;div class=&quot;form-group&quot;&gt;\r\n      &lt;label class=&quot;sr-only&quot; for=&quot;inputfile&quot;&gt;文件输入&lt;/label&gt;\r\n      &lt;input type=&quot;file&quot; id=&quot;inputfile&quot;&gt;\r\n   &lt;/div&gt;\r\n   &lt;div class=&quot;checkbox&quot;&gt;\r\n      &lt;label&gt;\r\n      &lt;input type=&quot;checkbox&quot;&gt; 请打勾\r\n      &lt;/label&gt;\r\n   &lt;/div&gt;\r\n   &lt;button type=&quot;submit&quot; class=&quot;btn btn-default&quot;&gt;提交&lt;/button&gt;\r\n&lt;/form&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;/body&gt;\r\n&lt;/html&gt;</pre><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-size: 12px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">结果如下所示：</p><div class=\"cover\" style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(214, 214, 214); margin: 0px; padding: 5px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"http://www.runoob.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/inlineform_demo.jpg\" alt=\"内联表单\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto;\"/></div><ul class=\"list\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 1em 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 16.7999992370605px; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><li style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 1em 1em; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.5em; line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 1em; background-image: url(http://www.runoob.com/wp-content/themes/runoob/assets/img/bullet.png); background-position: 0% 0.5em; background-repeat: no-repeat;\">默认情况下，Bootstrap 中的 input、select 和 textarea 有 100% 宽度。在使用内联表单时，您需要在表单控件上设置一个宽度。</li><li style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 1em 1em; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.5em; line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 1em; background-image: url(http://www.runoob.com/wp-content/themes/runoob/assets/img/bullet.png); background-position: 0% 0.5em; background-repeat: no-repeat;\">使用 class<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><em>.sr-only</em>，您可以隐藏内联表单的标签。</li></ul><h3 style=\"border: 0px; margin: 8px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 1.4em; font-weight: 700; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">水平表单</h3><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-size: 12px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">水平表单与其他表单不仅标记的数量上不同，而且表单的呈现形式也不同。如需创建一个水平布局的表单，请按下面的几个步骤进行：</p><ul class=\"list\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 1em 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 16.7999992370605px; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><li style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 1em 1em; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.5em; line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 1em; background-image: url(http://www.runoob.com/wp-content/themes/runoob/assets/img/bullet.png); background-position: 0% 0.5em; background-repeat: no-repeat;\">向父 &lt;form&gt; 元素添加 class<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><em>.form-horizontal</em>。</li><li style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 1em 1em; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.5em; line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 1em; background-image: url(http://www.runoob.com/wp-content/themes/runoob/assets/img/bullet.png); background-position: 0% 0.5em; background-repeat: no-repeat;\">把标签和控件放在一个带有 class<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><em>.form-group</em><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>的 &lt;div&gt; 中。</li><li style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 1em 1em; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.5em; line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 1em; background-image: url(http://www.runoob.com/wp-content/themes/runoob/assets/img/bullet.png); background-position: 0% 0.5em; background-repeat: no-repeat;\">向标签添加 class<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><em>.control-label</em>。</li></ul><pre class=\"prettyprint tryit\" style=\"border-width: 1px 1px 1px 4px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(221, 221, 221); margin: 15px auto; padding: 10px 15px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: 20px; font-family: &#39;courier new&#39;; word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background: url(http://www.runoob.com/images/codecolorer_bg.gif) 50% 0% rgb(251, 251, 251);\">&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;\r\n&lt;html&gt;\r\n&lt;head&gt;\r\n   &lt;title&gt;Bootstrap 实例 - 水平表单&lt;/title&gt;\r\n   &lt;link rel=&quot;stylesheet&quot; href=&quot;http://apps.bdimg.com/libs/bootstrap/3.3.0/css/bootstrap.min.css&quot;&gt;\r\n   &lt;script src=&quot;http://apps.bdimg.com/libs/jquery/2.1.1/jquery.min.js&quot;&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n   &lt;script src=&quot;http://apps.bdimg.com/libs/bootstrap/3.3.0/js/bootstrap.min.js&quot;&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n&lt;/head&gt;\r\n&lt;body&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;form class=&quot;form-horizontal&quot; role=&quot;form&quot;&gt;\r\n   &lt;div class=&quot;form-group&quot;&gt;\r\n      &lt;label for=&quot;firstname&quot; class=&quot;col-sm-2 control-label&quot;&gt;名字&lt;/label&gt;\r\n      &lt;div class=&quot;col-sm-10&quot;&gt;\r\n         &lt;input type=&quot;text&quot; class=&quot;form-control&quot; id=&quot;firstname&quot; \r\n            placeholder=&quot;请输入名字&quot;&gt;\r\n      &lt;/div&gt;\r\n   &lt;/div&gt;\r\n   &lt;div class=&quot;form-group&quot;&gt;\r\n      &lt;label for=&quot;lastname&quot; class=&quot;col-sm-2 control-label&quot;&gt;姓&lt;/label&gt;\r\n      &lt;div class=&quot;col-sm-10&quot;&gt;\r\n         &lt;input type=&quot;text&quot; class=&quot;form-control&quot; id=&quot;lastname&quot; \r\n            placeholder=&quot;请输入姓&quot;&gt;\r\n      &lt;/div&gt;\r\n   &lt;/div&gt;\r\n   &lt;div class=&quot;form-group&quot;&gt;\r\n      &lt;div class=&quot;col-sm-offset-2 col-sm-10&quot;&gt;\r\n         &lt;div class=&quot;checkbox&quot;&gt;\r\n            &lt;label&gt;\r\n               &lt;input type=&quot;checkbox&quot;&gt; 请记住我\r\n            &lt;/label&gt;\r\n         &lt;/div&gt;\r\n      &lt;/div&gt;\r\n   &lt;/div&gt;\r\n   &lt;div class=&quot;form-group&quot;&gt;\r\n      &lt;div class=&quot;col-sm-offset-2 col-sm-10&quot;&gt;\r\n         &lt;button type=&quot;submit&quot; class=&quot;btn btn-default&quot;&gt;登录&lt;/button&gt;\r\n      &lt;/div&gt;\r\n   &lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/form&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;/body&gt;\r\n&lt;/html&gt;</pre><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-size: 12px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-size: 12px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">结果如下所示：</p><div class=\"cover\" style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(214, 214, 214); margin: 0px; padding: 5px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"http://www.runoob.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/horizontalform_demo.jpg\" alt=\"水平表单\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto;\"/></div><p><br style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/></p><h2 class=\"tutheader\" style=\"border-width: 1px 0px 0px; border-top-style: solid; border-top-color: rgb(212, 212, 212); margin: 0px; padding: 5px 0px 0px; font-size: 1.8em; line-height: 1.8em; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">支持的表单控件</h2><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-size: 12px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Bootstrap 支持最常见的表单控件，主要是<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><em>input、textarea、checkbox、radio 和 select</em>。</p><h3 style=\"border: 0px; margin: 8px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 1.4em; font-weight: 700; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">输入框（Input）</h3><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-size: 12px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">最常见的表单文本字段是输入框 input。用户可以在其中输入大多数必要的表单数据。Bootstrap 提供了对所有原生的 HTML5 的 input 类型的支持，包括：<em>text、password、datetime、datetime-local、date、month、time、week、number、email、url、search、tel</em>和<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><em>color</em>。适当的<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><em>type</em><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>声明是必需的，这样才能让<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><em>input</em><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>获得完整的样式。</p><pre class=\"prettyprint tryit\" style=\"border-width: 1px 1px 1px 4px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(221, 221, 221); margin: 15px auto; padding: 10px 15px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: 20px; font-family: &#39;courier new&#39;; word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background: url(http://www.runoob.com/images/codecolorer_bg.gif) 50% 0% rgb(251, 251, 251);\">&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;\r\n&lt;html&gt;\r\n&lt;head&gt;\r\n   &lt;title&gt;Bootstrap 实例 - 输入框&lt;/title&gt;\r\n   &lt;link rel=&quot;stylesheet&quot; href=&quot;http://apps.bdimg.com/libs/bootstrap/3.3.0/css/bootstrap.min.css&quot;&gt;\r\n   &lt;script src=&quot;http://apps.bdimg.com/libs/jquery/2.1.1/jquery.min.js&quot;&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n   &lt;script src=&quot;http://apps.bdimg.com/libs/bootstrap/3.3.0/js/bootstrap.min.js&quot;&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n&lt;/head&gt;\r\n&lt;body&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;form role=&quot;form&quot;&gt;\r\n  &lt;div class=&quot;form-group&quot;&gt;\r\n    &lt;label for=&quot;name&quot;&gt;标签&lt;/label&gt;\r\n    &lt;input type=&quot;text&quot; class=&quot;form-control&quot; placeholder=&quot;文本输入&quot;&gt;\r\n  &lt;/div&gt;\r\n &lt;/form&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;/body&gt;\r\n&lt;/html&gt;</pre><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-size: 12px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">结果如下所示：</p><div class=\"cover\" style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(214, 214, 214); margin: 0px; padding: 5px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"http://www.runoob.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/inputs_demo.jpg\" alt=\"输入框\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto;\"/></div><h3 style=\"border: 0px; margin: 8px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 1.4em; font-weight: 700; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">文本框（Textarea）</h3><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-size: 12px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">当您需要进行多行输入的时，则可以使用文本框 textarea。必要时可以改变<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><em>rows</em><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>属性（较少的行 = 较小的盒子，较多的行 = 较大的盒子）。</p><pre class=\"prettyprint tryit\" style=\"border-width: 1px 1px 1px 4px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(221, 221, 221); margin: 15px auto; padding: 10px 15px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: 20px; font-family: &#39;courier new&#39;; word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background: url(http://www.runoob.com/images/codecolorer_bg.gif) 50% 0% rgb(251, 251, 251);\">&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;\r\n&lt;html&gt;\r\n&lt;head&gt;\r\n   &lt;title&gt;Bootstrap 实例 - 文本框&lt;/title&gt;\r\n   &lt;link rel=&quot;stylesheet&quot; href=&quot;http://apps.bdimg.com/libs/bootstrap/3.3.0/css/bootstrap.min.css&quot;&gt;\r\n   &lt;script src=&quot;http://apps.bdimg.com/libs/jquery/2.1.1/jquery.min.js&quot;&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n   &lt;script src=&quot;http://apps.bdimg.com/libs/bootstrap/3.3.0/js/bootstrap.min.js&quot;&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n&lt;/head&gt;\r\n&lt;body&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;form role=&quot;form&quot;&gt;\r\n  &lt;div class=&quot;form-group&quot;&gt;\r\n    &lt;label for=&quot;name&quot;&gt;文本框&lt;/label&gt;\r\n    &lt;textarea class=&quot;form-control&quot; rows=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;/textarea&gt;\r\n  &lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/form&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;/body&gt;\r\n&lt;/html&gt;</pre><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-size: 12px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">结果如下所示：</p><div class=\"cover\" style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(214, 214, 214); margin: 0px; padding: 5px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"http://www.runoob.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/textarea_demo.jpg\" alt=\"文本框\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto;\"/></div><h3 style=\"border: 0px; margin: 8px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 1.4em; font-weight: 700; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">复选框（（Checkbox）和单选框（Radio）</h3><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-size: 12px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">复选框和单选按钮用于让用户从一系列预设置的选项中进行选择。</p><ul class=\"list\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 1em 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 16.7999992370605px; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><li style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 1em 1em; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.5em; line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 1em; background-image: url(http://www.runoob.com/wp-content/themes/runoob/assets/img/bullet.png); background-position: 0% 0.5em; background-repeat: no-repeat;\">当创建表单时，如果您想让用户从列表中选择若干个选项时，请使用<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><em>checkbox</em>。如果您限制用户只能选择一个选项，请使用<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><em>radio</em>。</li><li style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 1em 1em; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.5em; line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 1em; background-image: url(http://www.runoob.com/wp-content/themes/runoob/assets/img/bullet.png); background-position: 0% 0.5em; background-repeat: no-repeat;\">对一系列复选框和单选框使用<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><em>.checkbox-inline</em><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>或<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><em>.radio-inline</em><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>class，控制它们显示在同一行上。</li></ul><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-size: 12px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">下面的实例演示了这两种类型（默认和内联）：</p><pre class=\"prettyprint tryit\" style=\"border-width: 1px 1px 1px 4px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(221, 221, 221); margin: 15px auto; padding: 10px 15px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: 20px; font-family: &#39;courier new&#39;; word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background: url(http://www.runoob.com/images/codecolorer_bg.gif) 50% 0% rgb(251, 251, 251);\">&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;\r\n&lt;html&gt;\r\n&lt;head&gt;\r\n   &lt;title&gt;Bootstrap 实例 - 复选框和单选按钮&lt;/title&gt;\r\n   &lt;link rel=&quot;stylesheet&quot; href=&quot;http://apps.bdimg.com/libs/bootstrap/3.3.0/css/bootstrap.min.css&quot;&gt;\r\n   &lt;script src=&quot;http://apps.bdimg.com/libs/jquery/2.1.1/jquery.min.js&quot;&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n   &lt;script src=&quot;http://apps.bdimg.com/libs/bootstrap/3.3.0/js/bootstrap.min.js&quot;&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n&lt;/head&gt;\r\n&lt;body&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;label for=&quot;name&quot;&gt;默认的复选框和单选按钮的实例&lt;/label&gt;\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;checkbox&quot;&gt;\r\n   &lt;label&gt;&lt;input type=&quot;checkbox&quot; value=&quot;&quot;&gt;选项 1&lt;/label&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;checkbox&quot;&gt;\r\n   &lt;label&gt;&lt;input type=&quot;checkbox&quot; value=&quot;&quot;&gt;选项 2&lt;/label&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;radio&quot;&gt;\r\n   &lt;label&gt;\r\n      &lt;input type=&quot;radio&quot; name=&quot;optionsRadios&quot; id=&quot;optionsRadios1&quot; \r\n         value=&quot;option1&quot; checked&gt; 选项 1\r\n   &lt;/label&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;radio&quot;&gt;\r\n   &lt;label&gt;\r\n      &lt;input type=&quot;radio&quot; name=&quot;optionsRadios&quot; id=&quot;optionsRadios2&quot; \r\n         value=&quot;option2&quot;&gt;\r\n         选项 2 - 选择它将会取消选择选项 1\r\n   &lt;/label&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;label for=&quot;name&quot;&gt;内联的复选框和单选按钮的实例&lt;/label&gt;\r\n&lt;div&gt;\r\n   &lt;label class=&quot;checkbox-inline&quot;&gt;\r\n      &lt;input type=&quot;checkbox&quot; id=&quot;inlineCheckbox1&quot; value=&quot;option1&quot;&gt; 选项 1\r\n   &lt;/label&gt;\r\n   &lt;label class=&quot;checkbox-inline&quot;&gt;\r\n      &lt;input type=&quot;checkbox&quot; id=&quot;inlineCheckbox2&quot; value=&quot;option2&quot;&gt; 选项 2\r\n   &lt;/label&gt;\r\n   &lt;label class=&quot;checkbox-inline&quot;&gt;\r\n      &lt;input type=&quot;checkbox&quot; id=&quot;inlineCheckbox3&quot; value=&quot;option3&quot;&gt; 选项 3\r\n   &lt;/label&gt;\r\n   &lt;label class=&quot;checkbox-inline&quot;&gt;\r\n      &lt;input type=&quot;radio&quot; name=&quot;optionsRadiosinline&quot; id=&quot;optionsRadios3&quot; \r\n         value=&quot;option1&quot; checked&gt; 选项 1\r\n   &lt;/label&gt;\r\n   &lt;label class=&quot;checkbox-inline&quot;&gt;\r\n      &lt;input type=&quot;radio&quot; name=&quot;optionsRadiosinline&quot; id=&quot;optionsRadios4&quot; \r\n         value=&quot;option2&quot;&gt; 选项 2\r\n   &lt;/label&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;/body&gt;\r\n&lt;/html&gt;</pre><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-size: 12px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-size: 12px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">结果如下所示：</p><div class=\"cover\" style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(214, 214, 214); margin: 0px; padding: 5px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"http://www.runoob.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/checkbox_demo.jpg\" alt=\"复选框和单选按钮\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto;\"/></div><h3 style=\"border: 0px; margin: 8px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 1.4em; font-weight: 700; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">选择框（Select）</h3><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-size: 12px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">当您想让用户从多个选项中进行选择，但是默认情况下只能选择一个选项时，则使用选择框。</p><ul class=\"list\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 1em 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 16.7999992370605px; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><li style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 1em 1em; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.5em; line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 1em; background-image: url(http://www.runoob.com/wp-content/themes/runoob/assets/img/bullet.png); background-position: 0% 0.5em; background-repeat: no-repeat;\">使用 &lt;select&gt; 展示列表选项，通常是那些用户很熟悉的选择列表，比如州或者数字。</li><li style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 1em 1em; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.5em; line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 1em; background-image: url(http://www.runoob.com/wp-content/themes/runoob/assets/img/bullet.png); background-position: 0% 0.5em; background-repeat: no-repeat;\">使用<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><em>multiple=&quot;multiple&quot;</em><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>允许用户选择多个选项。</li></ul><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-size: 12px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">下面的实例演示了这两种类型（select 和 multiple）：</p><pre class=\"prettyprint tryit\" style=\"border-width: 1px 1px 1px 4px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(221, 221, 221); margin: 15px auto; padding: 10px 15px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: 20px; font-family: &#39;courier new&#39;; word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background: url(http://www.runoob.com/images/codecolorer_bg.gif) 50% 0% rgb(251, 251, 251);\">&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;\r\n&lt;html&gt;\r\n&lt;head&gt;\r\n   &lt;title&gt;Bootstrap 实例 - 选择框&lt;/title&gt;\r\n   &lt;link rel=&quot;stylesheet&quot; href=&quot;http://apps.bdimg.com/libs/bootstrap/3.3.0/css/bootstrap.min.css&quot;&gt;\r\n   &lt;script src=&quot;http://apps.bdimg.com/libs/jquery/2.1.1/jquery.min.js&quot;&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n   &lt;script src=&quot;http://apps.bdimg.com/libs/bootstrap/3.3.0/js/bootstrap.min.js&quot;&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n&lt;/head&gt;\r\n&lt;body&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;form role=&quot;form&quot;&gt;\r\n   &lt;div class=&quot;form-group&quot;&gt;\r\n      &lt;label for=&quot;name&quot;&gt;选择列表&lt;/label&gt;\r\n      &lt;select class=&quot;form-control&quot;&gt;\r\n         &lt;option&gt;1&lt;/option&gt;\r\n         &lt;option&gt;2&lt;/option&gt;\r\n         &lt;option&gt;3&lt;/option&gt;\r\n         &lt;option&gt;4&lt;/option&gt;\r\n         &lt;option&gt;5&lt;/option&gt;\r\n      &lt;/select&gt;\r\n\r\n      &lt;label for=&quot;name&quot;&gt;可多选的选择列表&lt;/label&gt;\r\n      &lt;select multiple class=&quot;form-control&quot;&gt;\r\n         &lt;option&gt;1&lt;/option&gt;\r\n         &lt;option&gt;2&lt;/option&gt;\r\n         &lt;option&gt;3&lt;/option&gt;\r\n         &lt;option&gt;4&lt;/option&gt;\r\n         &lt;option&gt;5&lt;/option&gt;\r\n      &lt;/select&gt;\r\n   &lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/form&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;/body&gt;\r\n&lt;/html&gt;</pre><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-size: 12px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-size: 12px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">结果如下所示：</p><div class=\"cover\" style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(214, 214, 214); margin: 0px; padding: 5px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"http://www.runoob.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/select_demo.jpg\" alt=\"选择框\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto;\"/></div><p><br style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/></p><h2 class=\"tutheader\" style=\"border-width: 1px 0px 0px; border-top-style: solid; border-top-color: rgb(212, 212, 212); margin: 0px; padding: 5px 0px 0px; font-size: 1.8em; line-height: 1.8em; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">静态控件</h2><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-size: 12px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">当您需要在一个水平表单内的表单标签后放置纯文本时，请在 &lt;p&gt; 上使用 class<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><em>.form-control-static</em>。</p><pre class=\"prettyprint tryit\" style=\"border-width: 1px 1px 1px 4px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(221, 221, 221); margin: 15px auto; padding: 10px 15px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: 20px; font-family: &#39;courier new&#39;; word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background: url(http://www.runoob.com/images/codecolorer_bg.gif) 50% 0% rgb(251, 251, 251);\">&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;\r\n&lt;html&gt;\r\n&lt;head&gt;\r\n   &lt;title&gt;Bootstrap 实例 - 静态控件&lt;/title&gt;\r\n   &lt;link rel=&quot;stylesheet&quot; href=&quot;http://apps.bdimg.com/libs/bootstrap/3.3.0/css/bootstrap.min.css&quot;&gt;\r\n   &lt;script src=&quot;http://apps.bdimg.com/libs/jquery/2.1.1/jquery.min.js&quot;&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n   &lt;script src=&quot;http://apps.bdimg.com/libs/bootstrap/3.3.0/js/bootstrap.min.js&quot;&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n&lt;/head&gt;\r\n&lt;body&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;form class=&quot;form-horizontal&quot; role=&quot;form&quot;&gt;\r\n  &lt;div class=&quot;form-group&quot;&gt;\r\n    &lt;label class=&quot;col-sm-2 control-label&quot;&gt;Email&lt;/label&gt;\r\n    &lt;div class=&quot;col-sm-10&quot;&gt;\r\n      &lt;p class=&quot;form-control-static&quot;&gt;email@example.com&lt;/p&gt;\r\n    &lt;/div&gt;\r\n  &lt;/div&gt;\r\n  &lt;div class=&quot;form-group&quot;&gt;\r\n    &lt;label for=&quot;inputPassword&quot; class=&quot;col-sm-2 control-label&quot;&gt;密码&lt;/label&gt;\r\n    &lt;div class=&quot;col-sm-10&quot;&gt;\r\n      &lt;input type=&quot;password&quot; class=&quot;form-control&quot; id=&quot;inputPassword&quot; \r\n         placeholder=&quot;请输入密码&quot;&gt;\r\n    &lt;/div&gt;\r\n  &lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/form&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;/body&gt;\r\n&lt;/html&gt;</pre><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-size: 12px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">结果如下所示：</p><div class=\"cover\" style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(214, 214, 214); margin: 0px; padding: 5px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"http://www.runoob.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/staticcontrol_demo.jpg\" alt=\"静态控件\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto;\"/></div><p><br style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/></p><h2 class=\"tutheader\" style=\"border-width: 1px 0px 0px; border-top-style: solid; border-top-color: rgb(212, 212, 212); margin: 0px; padding: 5px 0px 0px; font-size: 1.8em; line-height: 1.8em; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">表单控件状态</h2><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-size: 12px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">除了<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><em>:focus</em><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>状态（即，用户点击 input 或使用 tab 键聚焦到 input 上），Bootstrap 还为禁用的输入框定义了样式，并提供了表单验证的 class。</p><h3 style=\"border: 0px; margin: 8px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 1.4em; font-weight: 700; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">输入框焦点</h3><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-size: 12px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">当输入框 input 接收到<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><em>:focus</em><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>时，输入框的轮廓会被移除，同时应用<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><em>box-shadow</em>。</p><h3 style=\"border: 0px; margin: 8px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 1.4em; font-weight: 700; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">禁用的输入框 input</h3><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-size: 12px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">如果您想要禁用一个输入框 input，只需要简单地添加<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><em>disabled</em><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>属性，这不仅会禁用输入框，还会改变输入框的样式以及当鼠标的指针悬停在元素上时鼠标指针的样式。</p><h3 style=\"border: 0px; margin: 8px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 1.4em; font-weight: 700; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">禁用的字段集 fieldset</h3><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-size: 12px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">对 &lt;fieldset&gt; 添加 disabled 属性来禁用 &lt;fieldset&gt; 内的所有控件。</p><h3 style=\"border: 0px; margin: 8px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 1.4em; font-weight: 700; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">验证状态</h3><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-size: 12px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Bootstrap 包含了错误、警告和成功消息的验证样式。只需要对父元素简单地添加适当的 class（<em>.has-warning、 .has-error 或 .has-success</em>）即可使用验证状态。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-size: 12px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">下面的实例演示了所有控件状态：</p><pre class=\"prettyprint tryit\" style=\"border-width: 1px 1px 1px 4px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(221, 221, 221); margin: 15px auto; padding: 10px 15px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: 20px; font-family: &#39;courier new&#39;; word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background: url(http://www.runoob.com/images/codecolorer_bg.gif) 50% 0% rgb(251, 251, 251);\">&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;\r\n&lt;html&gt;\r\n&lt;head&gt;\r\n   &lt;title&gt;Bootstrap 实例 - 表单控件状态&lt;/title&gt;\r\n   &lt;link rel=&quot;stylesheet&quot; href=&quot;http://apps.bdimg.com/libs/bootstrap/3.3.0/css/bootstrap.min.css&quot;&gt;\r\n   &lt;script src=&quot;http://apps.bdimg.com/libs/jquery/2.1.1/jquery.min.js&quot;&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n   &lt;script src=&quot;http://apps.bdimg.com/libs/bootstrap/3.3.0/js/bootstrap.min.js&quot;&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n&lt;/head&gt;\r\n&lt;body&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;form class=&quot;form-horizontal&quot; role=&quot;form&quot;&gt;\r\n   &lt;div class=&quot;form-group&quot;&gt;\r\n      &lt;label class=&quot;col-sm-2 control-label&quot;&gt;聚焦&lt;/label&gt;\r\n      &lt;div class=&quot;col-sm-10&quot;&gt;\r\n         &lt;input class=&quot;form-control&quot; id=&quot;focusedInput&quot; type=&quot;text&quot; \r\n            value=&quot;该输入框获得焦点...&quot;&gt;\r\n      &lt;/div&gt;\r\n   &lt;/div&gt;\r\n   &lt;div class=&quot;form-group&quot;&gt;\r\n      &lt;label for=&quot;inputPassword&quot; class=&quot;col-sm-2 control-label&quot;&gt;\r\n         禁用\r\n      &lt;/label&gt;\r\n      &lt;div class=&quot;col-sm-10&quot;&gt;\r\n         &lt;input class=&quot;form-control&quot; id=&quot;disabledInput&quot; type=&quot;text&quot; \r\n            placeholder=&quot;该输入框禁止输入...&quot; disabled&gt;\r\n      &lt;/div&gt;\r\n   &lt;/div&gt;\r\n   &lt;fieldset disabled&gt;\r\n      &lt;div class=&quot;form-group&quot;&gt;\r\n         &lt;label for=&quot;disabledTextInput&quot;  class=&quot;col-sm-2 control-label&quot;&gt;\r\n            禁用输入（Fieldset disabled）\r\n         &lt;/label&gt;\r\n         &lt;div class=&quot;col-sm-10&quot;&gt;\r\n            &lt;input type=&quot;text&quot; id=&quot;disabledTextInput&quot; class=&quot;form-control&quot; \r\n               placeholder=&quot;禁止输入&quot;&gt;\r\n         &lt;/div&gt;\r\n      &lt;/div&gt;\r\n      &lt;div class=&quot;form-group&quot;&gt;\r\n         &lt;label for=&quot;disabledSelect&quot;  class=&quot;col-sm-2 control-label&quot;&gt;\r\n            禁用选择菜单（Fieldset disabled）\r\n         &lt;/label&gt;\r\n         &lt;div class=&quot;col-sm-10&quot;&gt;\r\n            &lt;select id=&quot;disabledSelect&quot; class=&quot;form-control&quot;&gt;\r\n               &lt;option&gt;禁止选择&lt;/option&gt;\r\n            &lt;/select&gt;\r\n         &lt;/div&gt;\r\n      &lt;/div&gt;\r\n   &lt;/fieldset&gt;\r\n   &lt;div class=&quot;form-group has-success&quot;&gt;\r\n      &lt;label class=&quot;col-sm-2 control-label&quot; for=&quot;inputSuccess&quot;&gt;\r\n         输入成功\r\n      &lt;/label&gt;\r\n      &lt;div class=&quot;col-sm-10&quot;&gt;\r\n         &lt;input type=&quot;text&quot; class=&quot;form-control&quot; id=&quot;inputSuccess&quot;&gt;\r\n      &lt;/div&gt;\r\n   &lt;/div&gt;\r\n   &lt;div class=&quot;form-group has-warning&quot;&gt;\r\n      &lt;label class=&quot;col-sm-2 control-label&quot; for=&quot;inputWarning&quot;&gt;\r\n         输入警告\r\n      &lt;/label&gt;\r\n      &lt;div class=&quot;col-sm-10&quot;&gt;\r\n         &lt;input type=&quot;text&quot; class=&quot;form-control&quot; id=&quot;inputWarning&quot;&gt;\r\n      &lt;/div&gt;\r\n   &lt;/div&gt;\r\n   &lt;div class=&quot;form-group has-error&quot;&gt;\r\n      &lt;label class=&quot;col-sm-2 control-label&quot; for=&quot;inputError&quot;&gt;\r\n         输入错误\r\n      &lt;/label&gt;\r\n      &lt;div class=&quot;col-sm-10&quot;&gt;\r\n         &lt;input type=&quot;text&quot; class=&quot;form-control&quot; id=&quot;inputError&quot;&gt;\r\n      &lt;/div&gt;\r\n   &lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/form&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;/body&gt;\r\n&lt;/html&gt;</pre><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-size: 12px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-size: 12px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing